<section id="top" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-white py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 h-[34rem] w-[64rem] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 via-indigo-50 to-violet-100 opacity-80 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#e2e8f0_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#e2e8f0_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:48px_48px] opacity-30 [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_bottom,black,transparent_75%)]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto grid w-full max-w-6xl gap-14 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] lg:items-center">
    <div>
      <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-700 shadow-sm">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-600"></span>
        AI collaboration, documented
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-7 break-keep text-4xl font-black leading-[1.12] tracking-[-0.04em] text-slate-950 sm:text-6xl">
        AI와 함께 일하는 방법을,<br class="hidden sm:block">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-violet-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">실제 결과물로</span> 보여드립니다.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
        SaaS 구축 과정과 AI가 팀의 일하는 방식을 바꾼 기록. LEEDOX의 두 가지 실전 콘텐츠를 만나보세요.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <%= link_to "두 상품 살펴보기", "#products", class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-slate-950 px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-slate-900/10 transition hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-indigo-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2" %>
        <%= link_to "LEEDOX 소개", "#about", class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 transition hover:border-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-50 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-indigo-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-lg" aria-label="LEEDOX의 두 상품">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/50 blur-xl"></div>
      <div class="relative grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-2">
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-xl shadow-blue-950/10">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-xs font-black tracking-[0.16em] text-blue-700">CHATDOX</span>
            <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-600 font-black text-white">C</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-12 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400">BUILD WITH AI</p>
          <p class="mt-2 break-keep text-lg font-black leading-snug text-slate-950">AI와 함께<br>SaaS 구축하기</p>
          <div class="mt-5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-100"><div class="h-full w-3/4 rounded-full bg-blue-600"></div></div>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-violet-200 bg-slate-950 p-5 text-white shadow-xl shadow-violet-950/15 sm:translate-y-8 lg:translate-y-0 xl:translate-y-8">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-xs font-black tracking-[0.16em] text-violet-300">CLAUDOX</span>
            <span class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-violet-500 font-black">C</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-12 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500">WORK WITH AI</p>
          <p class="mt-2 break-keep text-lg font-black leading-snug">클로드가 들어온 날,<br>팀이 달라졌다</p>
          <div class="mt-5 flex gap-1.5"><span class="h-1.5 flex-1 rounded-full bg-violet-400"></span><span class="h-1.5 flex-1 rounded-full bg-slate-700"></span><span class="h-1.5 flex-1 rounded-full bg-slate-700"></span></div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
